    <p class="lead">Premium mobile and in-office notarization backed by meticulous process control and punctual arrivals.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="layout-container section-inner services-inner">
    <div class="services-grid" data-animate="services-grid">
      <article class="service-card service-card--primary glass-card" data-service="general-notarization" data-animate="service-card">
        <div class="service-card-header">
          <div class="service-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" role="presentation" focusable="false">
              <rect x="12" y="14" width="40" height="30" rx="6" ry="6" class="icon-stroke"></rect>
              <path d="M20 24h24" class="icon-stroke"></path>
              <path d="M20 32h24" class="icon-stroke"></path>
              <path d="M20 40h18" class="icon-stroke"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="service-badge">Most Requested</div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card-content">
          <h3>General Notarization</h3>
          <p class="service-lead">Precise acknowledgments, jurats, and oath administrations for personal and business documentation.</p>
          <ul class="service-highlights">
            <li>Real estate, POA, estate planning & corporate filings</li>
            <li>Document readiness review and signer ID verification</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="service-trust">
            <span class="service-trust-item">Same-day appointments available</span>
            <span class="service-trust-item">State ID verification & compliant seals</span>
            <span class="service-trust-item">Secure audit trail for every signing</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-meta">
            <span class="service-price">$15 per signature</span>
            <span class="service-turnaround">Same-day availability</span>
          </div>
          <a href="#booking" class="service-cta" data-cta="general-notarization">Book Notarization</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <div class="service-stack" data-animate="service-stack">
        <article class="service-card glass-card" data-service="mobile-notary" data-animate="service-card">
          <div class="service-card-header">
            <div class="service-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" role="presentation" focusable="false">
                <path d="M32 6c10.5 0 19 8.5 19 19 0 14.25-19 33-19 33S13 39.25 13 25c0-10.5 8.5-19 19-19z" class="icon-stroke"></path>
                <circle cx="32" cy="25" r="7" class="icon-stroke"></circle>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="service-badge">We Come To You</div>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card-content">
            <h3>Mobile Service</h3>
            <p class="service-lead">Professional signing appointments at your home, office, hospital, or secure third-party location.</p>
            <ul class="service-highlights">
              <li>Evenings, weekends, and rush requests accommodated</li>
              <li>Coverage across Lehigh Valley, PA & 50-mile service radius</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="service-meta">
              <span class="service-price">Travel fee calculated by zone</span>
              <span class="service-turnaround">90-minute arrival window</span>
            </div>
            <a href="#booking" class="service-cta service-cta--text" data-cta="mobile-service">Schedule Mobile Signing</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="service-card glass-card" data-service="loan-signings" data-animate="service-card">
          <div class="service-card-header">
            <div class="service-icon" aria-hidden="true">
